sense.gloss: (real) ability, true strength, merit, efficiency, competency

sdata.j: ↑我々↑↓われわれ↓の↑稼↑↓かせ↓ぎは|↑実力|↑↓じつりょく↓に↑比例↑↓ひれい↓している。
sdata.e: Our earnings are in proportion to our real ability.

sdata.j: やつらに|↑実力|↑↓じつりょく↓の↑差↑↓さ↓を↑見↑↓み↓せ↑付↑↓つ↓けてやった。
sdata.e: I showed them the difference of ability.

sdata.e: Bill won the match, not so much by good luck as by real ability.

sdata.e: Real ability wins in the end.

sdata.e: Both teams are well matched. The game will be an interesting one.

sdata.j: |↑実力|↑↓じつりょく↓だよ、|↑実力|↑↓じつりょく↓。
↑川↑↓かわ↓さんは↑家柄↑↓いえがら↓でなく|↑実力|↑↓じつりょく↓で↑出世↑↓しゅっせ↓しました。
sdata.e: Mr. Kawa made it to the top due to his own abilities, not because of his family.
